- Money? I got weekly pocket money. - No! You're joking!

643
01:11:11,000 --> 01:11:14,240
- 500法郎。——不!
- 500 francs. - No!

644
01:11:14,280 --> 01:11:17,680
1976年每周500法郎?
500 francs a week in 1976?

645
01:11:18,240 --> 01:11:22,320
-关于这个，是的。-你知道那有多重要吗?
- About that, yes. - Do you realise how much that was?

646
01:11:23,200 --> 01:11:27,280
也许你是一个小吉祥物，一个很酷的人
Maybe you were a little mascot, someone cool to be seen with -

647
01:11:27,320 --> 01:11:29,720
在马克西姆酒店和丽都酒店
at Maxim's and the Lido.

648
01:11:29,760 --> 01:11:34,080
-世界上最漂亮的男孩。-是的，“le petit garçon de Mort à Venise”
- The most beautiful boy in the world. - Yes, "le petit garçon de Mort à Venise."

649
01:11:34,120 --> 01:11:38,960
我是一个性对象，或者说是一个对象。大的游戏。
I was a sex object, or an object anyway. Big game.

650
01:11:39,880 --> 01:11:43,080
可以说，他们为你的公司付了钱。
They paid for your company, as it were.

651
01:11:43,120 --> 01:11:46,800
看在上帝的份上，我从来没有自己的钱，
For God's sake - I never had any money of my own,

652
01:11:46,840 --> 01:11:50,320
至少在我周游世界的时候不会。
at least not when I was travelling round the world.

653
01:11:51,320 --> 01:11:54,200
我太自以为是了。
It was so into my own ego.

654
01:11:54,240 --> 01:11:59,560
如果当时我知道今天的情况，我肯定不会去巴黎。
If I'd known then what I know today, I'd have said no to Paris.

655
01:12:09,160 --> 01:12:13,000
但这是非常重要的，Björn…
But it's of major importance, Björn...

656
01:12:15,120 --> 01:12:19,920
．..就今天的你和你如何看待自己而言，
...in terms of who you are today and of how you see yourself,

657
01:12:19,960 --> 01:12:22,800
那些破碎的梦想，
and of those shattered dreams,

658
01:12:22,840 --> 01:12:26,920
什么没发生，什么发生了。
and of what didn't happen, and what did.

659
01:12:28,000 --> 01:12:31,480
你不是一个简单的人Björn。
You're not an uncomplicated person, Björn.

660
01:12:34,880 --> 01:12:38,080
你是très compliqué。
Tu es très compliqué.

661
01:12:45,320 --> 01:12:47,680
亲爱的Bjorn……
Beloved Björn...

662
01:12:51,160 --> 01:12:55,920
-我一生的挚爱-我值得吗?
- The love of my life. - Do I deserve to be?

663
01:12:56,350 --> 01:12:58,520
你做的事情。
You do.

664
01:14:00,080 --> 01:14:02,840
-你好!嘿,亲爱的。
-Hi! -Hello, sweetie.

665
01:14:04,760 --> 01:14:07,840
-最近怎么样?-和往常一样。
- How are things? - Same as usual.

666
01:14:07,880 --> 01:14:11,200
同样的像往常一样吗?向上或向下?
Same as usual? Up or down?

667
01:14:11,240 --> 01:14:15,320
想尿尿，怕火车，没力气。
In need of a pee, scared of trains, lacking in strength.

668
01:14:15,350 --> 01:14:18,040
——一个小…-听起来很熟悉。
- A little... - That sounds familiar.

669
01:14:18,080 --> 01:14:22,840
你知道吗，到今年12月，我已经离开这里11年了?
Do you realise it's eleven years, this December, since I was last here?

670
01:14:22,880 --> 01:14:25,350
不要说!
Don't say that!

671
01:14:26,800 --> 01:14:31,840
真的有那么久了吗?我是说，这地方看起来…
Has it really been that long? I mean, this place looked...

672
01:14:31,880 --> 01:14:34,920
没有人来看我。
I haven't had anyone visiting.

673
01:14:34,960 --> 01:14:37,920
直到一年前，
Not until just over a year ago,

674
01:14:37,960 --> 01:14:42,320
杰西卡帮我打扫的时候
when Jessica helped me clean the place up.

675
01:14:48,960 --> 01:14:51,480
都挤在一起!
All squeezed together!

676
01:14:55,120 --> 01:15:00,200
-对"世界上最丑的婴儿"-是在"出生"下面吗?
- Right, "the ugliest baby in the world." - Is it in here, under "Births"?

677
01:15:02,520 --> 01:15:04,560
-在那儿!——是的。
- There it is! - Yup.

678
01:15:05,560 --> 01:15:09,350
“世界上最丑的孩子，我们美妙的女儿。”
"The ugliest baby in the world, our wonderful daughter."

679
01:15:10,600 --> 01:15:12,120
谢谢!
Thanks!

680
01:15:14,880 --> 01:15:17,280
你的内容。
You're content there.

681
01:15:20,680 --> 01:15:26,480
成为父亲是最可怕的事情。父亲应该做什么?
Becoming a father was the scariest thing ever. What are fathers supposed to do?

682
01:15:27,960 --> 01:15:34,680
几个月前我进了戏剧学校。
I'd got into drama school a few months earlier.

683
01:15:38,350 --> 01:15:41,520
我觉得我必须尽我所能做到最好。
I felt I had to do the best I possibly could.

684
01:15:41,560 --> 01:15:44,840
我最大的愿望是
And my biggest wish was

685
01:15:44,880 --> 01:15:51,240
你就不用经历我小时候所经历的
that you wouldn't have to go through what I went through as a child.

686
01:15:52,680 --> 01:15:57,120
要维持一个家庭，你需要两个人。
For a family to work, you need to be two people.

687
01:15:57,640 --> 01:16:02,040
这就是它崩溃的地方。喝了太多酒…
That's where it fell apart. Too much alcohol and...

688
01:16:02,080 --> 01:16:06,840
但我觉得我是个更健康的成年人
But I think I'm a healthier adult

689
01:16:06,880 --> 01:16:10,320
因为你们分居，而不是住在一起
due to your living apart, than if you'd lived together.

690
01:16:15,200 --> 01:16:18,120
-艾文到了。——是的。
- Elvin's arrived here. - Yes.

691
01:16:18,160 --> 01:16:21,040
这就是我们成为“好家庭”的时候。
That's when we became "the Good family".

692
01:16:21,080 --> 01:16:23,560
-我们成了“好家庭”?——是的。
- We became "the Good family"? - Yes.

693
01:16:25,960 --> 01:16:32,240
当我还是个孩子，甚至是十几岁的时候，你经常说，经常说:
When I was a child, even into my teens, you often said, very often:

694
01:16:32,280 --> 01:16:37,640
“如果你想知道什么，尽管问我。”
"If there's ever anything you want to know, just ask me."

695
01:16:37,680 --> 01:16:41,280
当你喝醉的时候…它是如此的神秘-
When you were drunk, too... It was so cryptic -

696
01:16:41,320 --> 01:16:44,760
我一直不知道你的问题是什么意思。
I never knew what questions you meant.

697
01:16:45,240 --> 01:16:49,760
你是想让我知道发生了什么事吗?
Was it that you wanted me to know what had happened?

698
01:16:50,680 --> 01:16:53,560
我不想让你孤单。
I didn't want you to be lonely.

699
01:16:54,800 --> 01:16:58,920
还有，不管你想知道什么…
Also, whatever you wanted to know...

700
01:17:01,120 --> 01:17:08,560
．..我会告诉你，即使不是实话，至少也要告诉你我的说法。
...I'd tell you, if not the truth, then at least my side of the story.

701
01:17:10,720 --> 01:17:13,320
你是如此美丽!
You're so beautiful!

702
01:17:18,920 --> 01:17:21,400
对不起。大男孩不哭。
Sorry. Big boys don't cry.

703
01:17:21,440 --> 01:17:26,520
我每次见到你，你都哭。总有些东西会感动你。
You cry almost every time I see you. Something always moves you.

704
01:17:26,560 --> 01:17:31,000
-是的，我是个敏感的家伙。-是的，那就做一个吧!
- Yes, I'm a sensitive bugger. - Yes, be one then!

705
01:17:34,440 --> 01:17:36,880
-我说什么了?-“我说什么?”
- What said I? - "What said I?"

706
01:17:38,560 --> 01:17:41,200
你知道吗，妈妈?
Do you know something, Mummy?

707
01:17:41,920 --> 01:17:47,880
艾文死了。他在花丛中。在天空中。
Elvin died. He's in the flowers. In the sky.

708
01:17:47,920 --> 01:17:50,520
在这张照片。
In the picture.

709
01:17:50,560 --> 01:17:53,920
在乐高。
In the Lego.

710
01:17:56,080 --> 01:17:58,560
这一切都是同时发生的。
And it all happened at once.

711
01:18:00,920 --> 01:18:03,920
-你觉得很难吗?——嗯。
- Do you find it hard? - Mm-hmm.

712
01:18:05,000 --> 01:18:08,960
-我拿了你的刀。-不，你说了。
- I took your knife. - Yes, you did.

713
01:18:11,080 --> 01:18:13,880
“这一切都是同时发生的。”
"And it all happened at once."

714
01:18:16,680 --> 01:18:23,320
那是1987年8月11日，罗宾三岁生日的第二天。
It was 11 August, 1987, the day after Robine's third birthday.

715
01:18:24,200 --> 01:18:27,240
在艾文死后差不多三个月。
Almost three months after Elvin died.

716
01:18:37,350 --> 01:18:40,680
我已经出去了。
I'd been out.

717
01:18:40,720 --> 01:18:43,080
那是5月17日。
It was 17 May.

718
01:18:45,080 --> 01:18:50,520
我在外面玩了很晚，我回到家，就睡着了。
I'd had a late night out, and I come home, and I fall asleep.

719
01:18:53,600 --> 01:18:59,400
她要带罗宾去幼儿园。
She's taking Robine to kindergarten.

720
01:18:59,440 --> 01:19:03,440
她把他放在我旁边的床上。
And she lays him next to me in bed.

721
01:19:04,920 --> 01:19:10,040
我睡得太少了。
I've had far, far too little sleep.

722
01:19:10,080 --> 01:19:13,160
我醉得一塌糊涂。
And I'm as drunk as hell.

723
01:19:21,920 --> 01:19:26,480
他躺在我旁边，我睡着了。
He's lying next to me, and I fall asleep.

724
01:19:28,920 --> 01:19:31,520
晕了过去。
Passed out.

725
01:19:32,720 --> 01:19:38,240
我被一声尖叫吵醒了，是她。
I'm woken up by a scream, and it's her.

726
01:19:47,350 --> 01:19:51,160
我能看见他躺在那里。他的嘴唇是蓝色的。
I can see him lying there. His lips are blue.

727
01:19:53,560 --> 01:19:59,000
然后我们拼命地，徒劳地，试图……
Then we desperately, and in vain, try to...

728
01:20:03,350 --> 01:20:05,200
．..他复活。
...resuscitate him.

729
01:20:13,640 --> 01:20:18,960
他们的诊断是婴儿猝死综合症
Their diagnosis is sudden infant death syndrome.

730
01:20:20,000 --> 01:20:23,320
但我的诊断是缺乏爱。
But my diagnosis is lack of love.

731
01:20:28,350 --> 01:20:32,320
我不能胜任。他必须承担太多的责任。
I wasn't up to it. And he had to take far too much responsibility.

732
01:20:32,350 --> 01:20:38,560
在他小小的肩膀上，他承载着我们全家的幸福。
On his tiny shoulders, he bore the whole of our family's happiness.

733
01:20:41,880 --> 01:20:44,520
但随着他的离去，一切都结束了。
But things gave way, with him.

734
01:21:00,280 --> 01:21:07,120
罗宾不仅失去了她的弟弟。她也失去了父亲。
Robine didn't only lose her little brother. She lost her father as well.

735
01:21:08,200 --> 01:21:12,800
我陷入了抑郁和酗酒之中。
I descended into depression and alcohol.

736
01:21:14,520 --> 01:21:16,240
自我毁灭……
Self-destruction...

737
01:21:17,560 --> 01:21:20,440
．..所有你能想到的方式。
...in all ways imaginable.

738
01:21:20,480 --> 01:21:25,680
这是一场自我炫耀。"可怜的我，我，我" -我，我，我。
It was an ego trip. "Poor me, me, me" - I, me, mine.

739
01:21:28,640 --> 01:21:31,480
然后你就变回孩子了。
And then you're back to being a child.

740
01:21:36,560 --> 01:21:38,800
一个孩子不能照顾自己的孩子。
A child can't look after a child.

741
01:21:44,760 --> 01:21:48,350
我们在一起8个月。
We had eight months together.

742
01:22:01,680 --> 01:22:04,480
他会……多大了?
He would have been... How old?

743
01:22:04,520 --> 01:22:07,480
他今天就32岁了。
He would have been 32 today.

744
01:22:11,200 --> 01:22:13,560
我想知道他的话听起来会是什么样子……
I wonder how he'd have sounded...

745
01:22:16,560 --> 01:22:19,880
．..他会有什么样的声音。
...what kind of voice he would've had.

746
01:22:24,080 --> 01:22:26,520
他的表情怎么样?
What about his expression?

747
01:22:30,720 --> 01:22:36,000
而这一切都取决于我作为一个父亲的表现。
And that would all have depended on how I'd acted as a father.

748
01:22:39,600 --> 01:22:42,520
因为他是我的儿子。
Because he was my boy.

749
01:22:48,600 --> 01:22:51,480
但事实是，我当时不在那里。
But the fact is, I wasn't there.

750
01:22:51,520 --> 01:22:57,520
如果我不出去，如果我表现得像个成年人，他就会活着。
If I hadn't gone out, if I'd behaved like an adult instead, he would be alive.

751
01:22:57,560 --> 01:23:02,880
如果我认真对待自己的责任，他今天应该还活着。
If I'd taken my responsibility seriously, he'd still be alive today.

752
01:23:06,480 --> 01:23:09,840
但一切从一开始就错了。
But everything was wrong from the start.

753
01:23:09,880 --> 01:23:13,720
我的生活。她的生活。
My life. Her life.

754
01:23:15,920 --> 01:23:18,800
真正疯狂的是你已经习惯了。
What's really insane is that you get used to it.

755
01:23:20,560 --> 01:23:23,280
你别指望……
You don't expect...

756
01:23:24,480 --> 01:23:27,280
．..这就是生活。
...that much from life.

757
01:23:28,200 --> 01:23:32,560
我真不知道该怎么表达。当你失去了那么多
I don't really know how to express it. When you've lost so much,

758
01:23:32,600 --> 01:23:39,350
它以自己独特的方式让生活变得更容易。
it somehow, in its own special way, makes life easier to live.

759
01:23:42,680 --> 01:23:46,560
好吧，我错过了，我错过了。好吧。
Okay - I missed this, I lost that. Okay.

760
01:23:47,960 --> 01:23:49,920
我失去了太多其他的东西。
I've lost so much else.

761
01:24:12,920 --> 01:24:17,520
艾文:3个月。罗宾:2年4个月。
Elvin: 3 months. Robine: 2 years, 4 months.

762
01:24:17,560 --> 01:24:22,720
桑娜:24年零9个月。Björn: 31年11个月。
Sanna: 24 years, 9 months. Björn: 31 years, 11 months.

763
01:24:44,920 --> 01:24:47,240
你曾经躺在草地上吗
Have you ever lain on the grass

764
01:24:47,280 --> 01:24:51,440
想象你不是在看太空，
and imagined you're not looking into space,

765
01:24:51,480 --> 01:24:55,880
但是你在观察下面是什么?
but you're observing what's down below?

766
01:25:00,960 --> 01:25:04,080
这是一种非常令人敬畏的感觉。
It's a pretty awe-inspiring feeling.

767
01:25:04,120 --> 01:25:09,680
我的意思是，当我们仰望星空时，我们是朝哪个方向看的?
I mean, when we look up at the stars, what direction are we looking in?

768
01:25:09,720 --> 01:25:16,120
我们是在向外看、向内看、向上看还是向下看?
Are we looking outwards, inwards, upwards, or downwards?

769
01:25:26,880 --> 01:25:30,560
我是说，我还在这，坐在这里，
I mean, I'm still around, I'm sitting here,

770
01:25:30,600 --> 01:25:36,160
世间的一切都是极不确定的
and everything worldly is extremely uncertain

771
01:25:36,200 --> 01:25:38,640
除非你有自己的信仰。
unless one has one's faith.

772
01:25:52,350 --> 01:25:57,880
当我看试镜时，
When I look at the screen test,

773
01:25:57,920 --> 01:26:01,080
在《威尼斯之死》的试镜中
shot at his audition for Death in Venice,

774
01:26:01,600 --> 01:26:04,320
我觉得很痛苦。
I find it painful.

775
01:26:04,350 --> 01:26:10,280
我可以处理这一切的结果，也可以处理他现在的样子。
I can deal with what it all resulted in, and with the person he's become today.

776
01:26:10,320 --> 01:26:18,320
但在电影中看到的——那个关键的转折点……
But witnessing it there on film - that crucial turning point...

777
01:26:18,350 --> 01:26:23,320
当我看到他这么不自在，
When I see how very ill at ease he feels,

778
01:26:23,350 --> 01:26:27,120
知道其他观众不知道的事情，
and, knowing things that other people watching this don't know,

779
01:26:27,160 --> 01:26:29,600
关于他是谁…
about the person he is...

780
01:26:29,640 --> 01:26:34,040
我们说的是一个非常敏感的男孩，非常害羞，
We're talking about an incredibly sensitive boy, really shy,

781
01:26:34,080 --> 01:26:36,720
一个根本不想去的人。
who doesn't even want to be there.

782
01:26:36,760 --> 01:26:41,840
然后他就得脱了衣服摆造型。
Then he's suddenly supposed to pose without his shirt.

783
01:26:41,880 --> 01:26:44,480
裸露对他来说不是…
Nudity to him isn't...

784
01:26:46,600 --> 01:26:49,880
他不想赤身裸体，也不想脱衣服。
He doesn't want to be naked, doesn't want to take his clothes off.

785
01:26:49,920 --> 01:26:52,640
这是令人痛苦的。
That was painful to watch.

786
01:26:52,680 --> 01:26:57,800
这就是我想要回到过去的地方问他奶奶她在做什么
That's where I want to go back in time and ask his granny what she's up to:

787
01:26:57,840 --> 01:27:01,080
“住手!离这孩子远点。”
"Stop it! Leave the lad alone."

788
01:27:02,640 --> 01:27:05,880
这是错误的。你不能这样对孩子。
It's wrong. You don't do that to children.

789
01:27:33,080 --> 01:27:35,760
达秋……?达秋!
Tadzio...? Tadzio!

790
01:28:09,600 --> 01:28:13,680
“安静，不要再说严厉的话。
"Be still, no more harsh words.

791
01:28:14,840 --> 01:28:17,640
“我已经所剩无几了。
"There's not much left of me.

792
01:28:21,000 --> 01:28:24,200
“不要为我哭泣。
"Don't cry over me.

793
01:28:24,240 --> 01:28:27,720
“已经没有什么火需要扑灭了。
"There's no longer any fire to put out.

794
01:28:29,560 --> 01:28:35,280
“我不再清楚自己是什么，不是什么。
"I no longer have a sense of what I am and what I'm not.

795
01:28:38,600 --> 01:28:43,200
”我环顾四周。是我吗?
"I look around. Is that me?

796
01:28:44,120 --> 01:28:45,640
“也?”
"Or that?"

797
01:28:45,680 --> 01:28:47,440
达秋!
Tadzio!

798
01:28:53,960 --> 01:28:57,640
“我变得越来越隐形了。
"I'm becoming more and more invisible.

799
01:28:57,680 --> 01:29:00,520
“我已经放弃了我曾经拥有的一切。
"I've given away all I ever had.

800
01:29:03,360 --> 01:29:05,560
“但我不会死的。
"But I'm not going to die.

801
01:29:08,440 --> 01:29:11,240
“剩下的是一扇门。
"What remains: a door.

802
01:29:12,720 --> 01:29:16,680
“我没有死，我只是消失了。
"I don't die, I just disappear.

803
01:29:17,960 --> 01:29:21,000
“也许,我会唤醒。
"Maybe, I'll reawaken.

804
01:29:22,520 --> 01:29:26,680
“那我就回去找你。”
"Then I will return to look for you."

